Xoops Engine code without legacy code

/engine
The root directory for Xoops Engine code

/engine/docs
Documents

/engine/htdocs
Web docroot

/engine/lib
Libraries

/engine/var
System variable data

/engine/usr
User or community contributed components, including apps/modules, plugins, applets, themes, etc.

/engine/usr/apps
Xoops Engine apps, i.e. applications following new MVC

/engine/user/modules
Non MVC style modules

/engine/usr/plugins
Plugin folders

/engine/usr/applets
Applet folders

/engine/usr/themes
Theme folders
